01:20:44,415 --> 01:20:47,085
Jesse, aku tahu kau di sana,
Aku bisa mencium popcorn.

1118
01:20:48,503 --> 01:20:50,463
Jesse, ayolah. Buka.

1119
01:20:59,181 --> 01:21:02,601
Aku mencoba meneleponmu.
